column10:
I really liked the game in the beginning, when i first bought the game, because it was fun and interesting to harvest all that oil and gas. However when you have bin playing it for a week or two, and you have finished all the different campaigns, then you get bored really quick, as it lacks different things that make each level and campaign different from each other. 

Though if repetitive gameplay is something for you, then this game is great, and you should definitely try this game. (~; 

By Mads Pedersen
